You notice a few things on the desk: a spellbook and a crystal ball on a silver stand. The spellbook looks ancient and important, while the crystal ball seems to glow with a faint, mysterious light. The crystal ball sits on a stand that hums softly, as if it’s alive with magic.

Exits lead up to an ornate door and down to the spiral staircase that leads back to the Tower Entrance.

